,(748,'실제로 여성의 권리와 의무를 존중하는 제 의견은 이러한 단순한 원칙에서 자연스럽게 흘러나오는 것 같아서 거의 불가능하다고 생각하지만, 여러분의 훌륭한 헌법을 만든 일부 확대 된 마음은 저와 일치 할 것입니다.','my opinion, indeed, respecting the rights and duties of woman, seems to flow so naturally from these simple principles, that i think it scarcely possible, but that some of the enlarged minds who formed your admirable constitution, will coincide with me.',1792,2001,'253','[\'my\', \'opinion\', \'indeed\', \'respecting\', \'the\', \'rights\', \'and\', \'duties\', \'of\', \'woman\', \'seems\', \'to\', \'flow\', \'so\', \'naturally\', \'from\', \'these\', \'simple\', \'principles\', \'that\', \'think\', \'it\', \'scarcely\', \'possible\', \'but\', \'that\', \'some\', \'of\', \'the\', \'enlarged\', \'minds\', \'who\', \'formed\', \'your\', \'admirable\', \'constitution\', \'will\', \'coincide\', \'with\', \'me\']',22),(749,'나의 독수리와 나의 뱀이 아니었더라면 주께서 주의 빛과 여정에 지치셨을 것입니다.','thou wouldst have wearied of thy light and of the journey, had it not been for me, mine eagle, and my serpent.',1887,2008,'110','[\'thou\', \'wouldst\', \'have\', \'wearied\', \'of\', \'thy\', \'light\', \'and\', \'of\', \'the\', \'journey\', \'had\', \'it\', \'not\', \'been\', \'for\', \'me\', \'mine\', \'eagle\', \'and\', \'my\', \'serpent\']',21),(750,'프랑스에서는 의심할 여지없이 유럽 어느 지역보다 더 일반적인 지식의 확산이 이루어지고 있으며, 저는 이것이 남녀 사이에 오랫동안 지속되어 온 사회적 교류에 기인한다고 생각합니다.','in france, there is undoubtedly a more general diffusion of knowledge than in any part of the european world, and i attribute it, in a great measure, to the social intercourse which has long subsisted between the sexes.',1792,2001,'219','[\'in\', \'france\', \'there\', \'is\', \'undoubtedly\', \'more\', \'general\', \'diffusion\', \'of\', \'knowledge\', \'than\', \'in\', \'any\', \'part\', \'of\', \'the\', \'european\', \'world\', \'and\', \'attribute\', \'it\', \'in\', \'great\', \'measure\', \'to\', \'the\', \'social\', \'intercourse\', \'which\', \'has\', \'long\', \'subsisted\', \'between\', \'the\', \'sexes\']',22),(751,'그러나